### Get list of all customers
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/customers

### Get single customer
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/customers/1

### Create a new customer
POST  http://localhost:5000/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Arizona",
  "countryId": 1
}

### Update a customer
PUT  http://localhost:5000/api/v1/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Florida"
}

### Delete a customer
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/v1/customers/1